author: Daniel Peters
title: Malcolm Turnbull issues stern warning to Coalition party | Daily Mail Online
text: 'Disunity is death': Malcolm Turnbull warns his party to come together - as MPs fear Tony Abbott is preparing for a 'fight to the death' after being blamed for government's dire polls Malcolm Turnbull has reportedly warned his party that 'disunity is death' He made the comments during a Coalition partyroom meeting on Tuesday Senior MP said it was a 'fight to the death' between Tony Abbott and Mr Turnbull Mr Abbott called for an immigration crackdown and slashing of electricity bills Prime Minister blamed him for the coalition's worst Newspoll result in two years
